content:
Hi everyone! The next Dataverse community call is next Tuesday, September 2 at 2pm UTC (10am Eastern) (see in your time zone).

Yijia (Jenna) Qi from UNC will talk about her research on data deletion and retention practices, and Bikramjit Channa from Borealis will talk about AI bot traffic and how he and colleagues have addressed it.

Join the call by checking visiting https://dataverse.org/community-calls to get the Zoom link and the meeting agendas and notes.
